summary: Bryce Harper has been making headlines both on and off the field. On the field, he had a four-hit performance against the Diamondbacks on June 22. Off the field, he debuted Wawa-inspired cleats, which he wore during the game where he appeared to mimic a hawk's hunting technique. Additionally, Harper showed his support for his former team, the Tennessee Volunteers, by wearing their jersey to the game. Other news stories highlight a recent interview with Cole Hamels, who reflected on hitting Harper with a pitch in 2012 and Harper's wife, Kayla, capturing adorable moments of her family at a recent concert.

name: Taylor Swift Travis Kelce
summary: Taylor Swift surprised her London audience during her Eras Tour by bringing on stage Kansas City Chiefs tight end Travis Kelce. Kelce's appearance was particularly unexpected and delighted fans, as it marked the first time he had joined Swift on stage at one of her concerts. The moment was captured on camera and widely shared on social media, with fans praising Swift's ability to bring together different worlds and create memorable experiences for her audience. The symbolism of Kelce's appearance, a football player on a music stage, has also sparked discussion among fans, with some interpreting it as a nod to Swift's own journey from country music to pop stardom.

USA Basketball has announced the finalists for its 2024 USA Men's U17 National Team. The schedule for the Paris Olympics and exhibitions has been released by USA Basketball. Team USA has announced its Women's Olympic Rugby Sevens Team for Paris 2024. Gymnastics City USA 2024 in Minneapolis will feature the USA Gymnastics Championships and Gymnastics for All. Ralph Lauren has unveiled the uniforms for Team USA. Despite a "missed opportunity,"Caitlin Clark will not participate in the LA Olympics this year. Finally, the CDC has released its weekly US Map: Influenza Summary Update.
